<Layout>

  <!-- hero -->

  <section class="section">

    <div class="container">

      <div class="top">

        <p class="meta">
          issue 001
        </p>

        <p class="meta">
          shreyash sharma
        </p>

        <p class="meta">
          2026<br />
          india / worldwide
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="hero-grid">

        <div>
           <h1 class="display hero-title">

           building fashion,<br />
           commerce &<br />
           intelligence systems.

</h1>

        </div>

        <div class="hero-image">
    <img
    src="/images/sex2.jpg"
    alt="campaign image"
    />
    </div>
      </div>

      <div class="editorial">

        <p>
          technology rarely possesses identity.

          most digital products are designed
          to function.

          few are designed to be remembered.

          this body of work explores how
          systems, brands and intelligence
          can coexist within the same
          cultural framework.
        </p>

        <p>
          from luxury commerce to artificial
          intelligence, each project
          investigates the relationship
          between design, infrastructure
          and permanence.

          systems should feel considered.

          systems should feel inevitable.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

